# Speech-to-Text API

---

## Syarat

- Docker & Docker Compose
- _(opsional)_ Python 3.10+ & pip — untuk test rekaman mikrofon lokal

---

## Start

```bash
docker compose up --build
```

Base url : `http://127.0.0.1:8000`.

Stop Docker compose:

```bash
docker compose down
```

---

## API Endpoints

### `POST /transcribe` — Transkripsi Audio

Upload file audio, dapatkan hasil transkripsi dalam JSON.

**Format yang didukung:** `.wav`, `.mp3`, `.flac`, `.m4a`

**Contoh dengan curl:**

```bash
curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/transcribe \
  -F "file=@rekaman.wav"
```

**Response:**

```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "json_file": "./output_transcriptions/transcript_20260710_214328.json",
  "text": "beras 2 kilo harga 25.000",
  "confidence": -0.2341,
  "no_speech": 0.0123
}
```

| Field | Keterangan |
|---|---|
| `text` | Hasil transkripsi teks |
| `confidence` | jika skor mendekati 0 akurasi model lebih baik |
| `no_speech` | Probabilitas tidak ada suara 0–1, makin kecil makin bagus |

### `GET /transcripts` Get All transcripts

```bash
curl http://127.0.0.1:8000/transcripts
```

### `GET /transcripts/{filename}` Get Detail transcripts
```bash
curl http://127.0.0.1:8000/transcripts/transcript_20260710_214328.json
```

---

## Test Rekaman Mikrofon (Opsional)

Script `test_mic.py` merekam audio 5 detik dari mikrofon lokal lalu mengirim ke API.

```bash
pip install sounddevice scipy requests
python test_mic.py
```

---

## Struktur Proyek

```
.
├── compose.yml              # Docker Compose config
├── test_mic.py              # Script test rekaman mikrofon
├── ml-service/
│   ├── Dockerfile
│   ├── main.py              # FastAPI app endpoint definitions
│   ├── whisper_audio.py     # Whisper transcription logic
│   ├── requirements.txt
│   └── output_transcriptions/  # Saved transcript
└── output_transcriptions/      # Volume mount dari container
```
